source.name: Maryland Male Labor Force Projections: 1970-2040
source.description:
Historical and Projected Male Labor Force in Maryland and its Jurisdictions, 1970-2040.
Projecte numbers are rounded to the nearest 10.
Prepared by the Maryland Department of Planning, April 2012.
